m property is required by this library.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_00ab2cb485e8e63a016a3fef592c108190ada288dfea768b3d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1002, "output": 825, "cacheRead": 27136, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 28963, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782574928178, "responseId": "resp_00ab2cb485e8e63a016a3fef50e3f0819095637cf04490040b"}}
